metadata.description: Chill Cowboy Country Club is the exclusive Community for fans, artists, brands, and anyone who has an interest in Country Music to celebrate all that is great about the industry. Through our use of membership NFTs, we can best ensure members, and members only, receive unique benefits such as members-only live events, merchandise, unreleased music and behind-the-scenes access to Country Music superstars. We are a space for those who love Country Music to hang out with others who share that love, have unrivaled live and interactive experiences, and learn more about the dynamic capabilities of Web3 technology.
